      "comment_id" : 117552209,
      "content_license" : "CC BY-SA 4.0",
      "body" : "How can you go about escaping whole <i>tags</i>? I want to do something like <code>{@literal {@code ...}}</code> (basically show the text &quot;{@code ...}&quot;) which Eclipse (falsely??) interprets as <code>{@code ...}}</code>."
