  "title" : "How can you escape the @ character in javadoc?",
  "body" : "<p>How can I escape the <code>@</code> symbol in javadoc? I am trying to use it inside a <code>{@code}</code> tag, which is inside <code>&lt;pre&gt;</code> tags.</p>\n\n<p>I already tried the html escape <code>&amp;#64;</code> sequence, but that didn't work.</p>\n"
